Enum CommentaryItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CommentaryItem>
      • com.intel.fightclub.dialog.coach.commentary.CommentaryItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Queryable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<CommentaryItem>

    public enum CommentaryItem
extends java.lang.Enum<CommentaryItem>
implements Queryable
    Items that are included in commentary events. It does NOT include all Speed, Pace or Length units.
